  "description": "This individual is a broad-shouldered human of middle years, marked by bronze skin and steady brown eyes set beneath heavy, work-worn brows. Black hair is kept in a plain, practical cut that leaves the face unobstructed and emphasizes a square jawline. Thickened fingers and prominent knuckles attest to long service in manual trade, while fine creases at the mouth and eyes record a life spent in close conversation and low light. The overall impression is durable, attentive, and accustomed to maintaining order at arm’s reach.",
